In addition: Warning message:
In grDevices:::png("/tmp/RtmpY0wRLe/26bdb48e96ab4a4b9ab8e49c79b53183.png",  :
unable to open connection to X11 display ''  
</code></li>
  <li>PNGs also donâ€™t work unless you add <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">type="cairo"</code> or use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">xvfb-run</code> to run with a Virtual X11 frame buffer.</li>
</ul>
